# Frontend — implemented in Phase 9 (NOT YET BUILT).
#
# REQUIREMENT (carry-forward): build a VERY HIGH-QUALITY frontend.
#   - Framework: React (Vite) — chosen for the polished "full product" deliverable (decisions.md D-36).
#   - Must include (FR 6.5): welcome message, 3 clickable example questions,
#     always-visible disclaimer "Facts-only. No investment advice.",
#     input field, response area (answer + clickable citation + "Last updated from sources: <date>" footer).
#   - Wire to: POST /api/query, GET /api/examples, GET /api/meta.
#   - Quality bar: clean design system, responsive, accessible (semantic HTML,
#     ARIA labels, keyboard nav), loading + error states, response-type styling
#     (factual / refusal / scope / no-source / PII).
#
# Do not implement until Phase 9 (prerequisite: Phase 8 API hardening).
